    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0

    v2 = ((v0 + wp.sin(v1 + 0.23)) * ((tmp + 0.65 / tmp + 0.46) * (v1 + 0.15 * v0 + 0.25)))
    v1 = (((v0 + 0.34 * v0 + 0.48) + (v2 + 0.87 * tmp + 0.90)) * 0.11)
